thread.title: Andrew Rowley
thread.title_full: Spa Store Australia reviewed by Andrew Rowley

author: Andrew Rowley
title: Andrew Rowley
text: I recently purchased several items for my Vortex spa and was surprised at how easy it was to find and order exactly what I needed without having to plough through page after page of non spa specific items. Who needs to visit a spa shop when there is such a great option available!
